*                                                                          *
*  Memory tracing Example:                                                 *
*                                                                          *
****************************************************************************

This example demonstrates use of the memory utilities in a SAMRAI application. 
It allocates 1 MB chunks of double arrays until the application runs out
of memory.  

The files included in this directory are as follows:
 
          main.C         -  example main program
 
COMPILE and RUN
---------------
Compile:  make     
Run:      ./memcheck                  
 
